{
  "stem": "1029.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were like so conspicuous, it's unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We didn't have any young people around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All the young people were conscripted into the workforce.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of the other young people were there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were practically hostages with their mothers and sisters there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How can they-- they go?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We couldn't go anywhere.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were-- we were-- there was just nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We couldn't do.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we weren't violent people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we didn't say, all right.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We're going to shoot our way out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And if we die, we die.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we'll take a couple with them, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We didn't even think of such a thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We just didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But that's the way it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we never-- we went through Vienna.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we went to another one of these train stations.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm not exactly sure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we went to Strasshof, that was a bad trip.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A lot of people died, maybe three or four.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then after a while, you know, we saw so much death that we-- our hearts became hardened.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we became jaded.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We-- when somebody died, it didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They just died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They-- we called them lucky, and they died.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we can't kill ourselves, because first of all, we are chicken to kill ourselves, or we just thought about maybe we'll be saved.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Or-- And we children, we didn't think on such lines, again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But there were a lot of people who committed suicide, but-- we-- a lot of intellectuals and rich people committed suicide who couldn't take--",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They just killed themselves with a pill or something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had some pills hidden away or something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Cyanide-- not cyanide-- arsenic, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had a couple of people who had drugstores.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Partikcak ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Partaka ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they just killed themselves with these things, and-- not-- not violently with knives or shooting.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "First of all, we didn't have anything to do that, you know, so--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This train ride wasn't as bad as the train ride from Strasshof to Belsen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was really bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, that train ride was, oh.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But this train ride, you know, about three or four diabetics died on our-- in our wagon.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It wasn't so bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It wasn't as tight-- as tightly fitted as they did it in Hungary from Saigon.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it was pretty tight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But-- only three or four people died.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were mainly diabetics.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we arrived, they-- they separated the men from the women.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took us immediately for a bath-- showers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They made us all undress.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everybody tried to keep their clothes, you know, in their little clumps so they recognized it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my mother was afraid for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She didn't let me go with the men.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So she kept me with the women.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I was the only boy with a multitude of naked women.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, to a young kid to see all these naked-- I never even saw my mother naked, practically.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Never mind all these old, young, skinny, fat, ugly, beautiful.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They're all-- and it's-- and every-- everything was so depressing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It wasn't-- it was dreamlike.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was-- they all took us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then they all washed us like they washed cattles, you know, and things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They didn't hose us or anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But we stood under the showers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And everybody was so violated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know, all the women, I could see them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were so-- and then there were men gazing at them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they didn't look at them after a lot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Even they were ashamed, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they just-- it was-- it was just a humiliating experience for everybody, which is unbelievably humiliating.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "To me, of course, it's probably left me scarred.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It must have left me scarred.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I don't know how.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But it-- it must left me, because I was a little boy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And-- but I was with my mother, and I survived it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then so as soon as we are finished, they made us get dressed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they powdered us with DDT, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They put DDT right to our bodies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, now we know DDT is toxic, and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in those days, they figured DDT, you know, just got rid of lice.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they powdered us and so on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- a-- and we got dressed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we feeled refreshed, [LAUGHS] if you could call it refreshed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- then they stuffed us into the cattle car.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was unbelievable because it was almost impossible to breathe, we were so tight.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and the-- and the windows weren't open.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the-- and the-- the windows, with-- they were covered with these-- with this wires, you know, stinging wires.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
